1. *Pažnje* molim! (Attention please!)
2. Na času treba da obratite *pažnju*. (You need to pay attention in class.)
3. *Pažnje* vozačima, na putu ima radova. (Attention drivers, roadworks ahead.)
4. Molim te, budi *pažljiv* dok voziš. (Please be careful while driving.)
5. Ona obraća *pažnju* na detalje. (She pays attention to details.)
6. *Pažnja* na pse koji lutaju ulicama. (Beware of stray dogs.)
7. Nije mi bilo dovoljno *pažnje* posvećenoj mom projektu. (I didn't receive enough attention to my project.)
8. Učenici su bili *pažljivi* tokom časa. (The students were careful during class.)
9. *Pažljivo* pročitaj uputstva pre nego što počneš. (Read the instructions carefully before you start.)
10. Oni su *pažljivo* planirali svoj budžet. (They carefully planned their budget.)